data.description: All brick basement ranch with gorgeous views on 6.7 acres! This spacious home features a master on the main floor plan, gleaming hardwood floors, a huge kitchen with a unique island, tons of cabinets, Cambria Quartz counter tops, tongue and groove ceiling, recessed lighting and a wall of pantry space. Storage abounds in this home which also offers new windows, large laundry room, basement family room and an additional two bedrooms and full bathroom. Enjoy life outside with patio space, a 20'x40' in-ground pool and pool house, and 6.7 acres which provides room to roam. This home truly has it all and is move in ready. Schedule your private showing today!
